<blockquote>
 <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1"/>
 This sign can be used to mean such things as enthusiasm, motivation, 
			and/or caffeine. (No, I'm not making that "caffeine" bit up. The 
			"Starbucks" crowd have to have ways of discussing their habits and 
			it seems they get their daily motivation from a cup of
 <a href="../c/coffee.htm" style="text-decoration: none">
  coffee
 </a>
 .)
 <br/>
 <br/>
 Rub your hands together "enthusiastically."
 <br/>
 <br/>
 ENTHUSIASM = "motivate"
 <br/>
 <img border="0" height="320" src="../../signjpegs/e/enthusiasm-17.jpg" width="275"/>
 <img border="0" height="320" src="../../signjpegs/e/enthusiasm-18.jpg" width="275"/>
 <img border="0" height="320" src="../../signjpegs/e/enthusiasm-19.jpg" width="275"/>
 <img border="0" height="320" src="../../signjpegs/e/enthusiasm-20.jpg" width="275"/>
