   <br/>
   Note:
   <br/>
   Often the concept of "motivation" could best be signed by using the 
			sign REASON, as in "What was your motivation for learning sign 
			language?"
   <br/>
   See:
   <a href="../r/reason.htm">
    REASON
   </a>
   <br/>
  </p>
